{"tid":1710981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔敢出黎既人，打個電話可以嗎？","createTime":"2019-11-12T09:28:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T11:13:28.000Z","uid":706,"like":276,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"1a8afd36ecf8a2bd3509d8895201cae01b5181fb","tid":1710981,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:28:21.000Z","msg":"雖然大家都未必係該國國民，但係如果大家一齊打去領事館求助，我相信領事館點都會report返比個國家知，會有當地傳媒報導<br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以一人打一個電話過去，以最無助既方式求助，香港人正面臨被攻擊及屠殺？唔係危機，唔係可能，已經係事實<br />\n<br />\n打個電話去，完全無成本無危險，唔會被秋後算帳，唔會有人知，出唔到黎既人，可唔可以盡你既能力救香港人？<br />\n<br />\n可能唔work，有無其他方法可以比所有人出一分力？<br />\n<br />\nList係公海copy，好似話五點收工，聽日大家一齊打去求助<br />\n<br />\n英國駐香港總領事館 +852 2901 3000<br />\n美國駐香港及澳門總領事館 +852 2523 9011<br />\n日本駐香港總領事館 +852 2522 1184<br />\n大韓民國駐香港總領事館2529 4141"},{"pid":"5022007b1108bc87afbc49ca636f5fea467ac02b","tid":1710981,"uid":147916,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:28:59.000Z","msg":"⚠轉出去⚠<br />\n❗大學 Lab 善用化學品反抗❗<br />\n❗HNO3❗<br />\n❗Mg❗<br />\n❗NH4NO3❗<br />\n❗NaOH❗<br />\n❗ANFO❗<br />\n❗ANSU❗"},{"pid":"222ed19295a25b092baecb289211e226b6de8111","tid":1710981,"uid":330472,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:29:05.000Z","msg":"香港人報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要攬炒，出去燒藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自然唔搞中大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70af01a879634b7a66e9ebeed9b711c27a2878d6","tid":1710981,"uid":248394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:31:03.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"458df691a0273a9b86290d48fc99df7c170e6356","tid":1710981,"uid":248394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:31:14.000Z","msg":"打！"},{"pid":"6f1d21df620f4cc6aacb50dc03cb70b1b3b4cd49","tid":1710981,"uid":248394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:31:27.000Z","msg":"打！"},{"pid":"47e993b6d1b4f9905830fe3ddf039500fca18a2d","tid":1710981,"uid":268537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:31:52.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"1ad7dd38e1bb518bdce351cca5267c82339ff940","tid":1710981,"uid":706,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:33:26.000Z","msg":"我知人地唔會受理，但我希望可以將依個咁恐怖既事實赤裸裸咁傳比外國，你見到有人比人打，你可能怕，可能唔知咩事，所以唔幫手，但如果有人直接向你求救，你可能會見義勇為，因為你無藉口唔幫<br />\n尤其是英國<br />\n<br />\n如果大家覺得有用，請幫手宣傳同推，如果覺得無用，請幫手諗下有咩方法可以令唔敢上戰場既人幫手<br />\n我知道已經有好多任務可以做，但係Twitter我諗外國已經睇到盲目，而且只係當新聞咁睇，直接向國際求救效果可以好唔同"},{"pid":"e2716da64934e462b3dbf7e5e7f3c96bf77955ee","tid":1710981,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:34:37.000Z","msg":"請打去領事館向國際求助"},{"pid":"99c4eb0712d0e01f138cb31f5a4a7c8c0b08cc7b","tid":1710981,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:35:01.000Z","msg":"請11月13日一齊打電話求助"},{"pid":"8fa0b5110e2a30e1286a2be30948cbd1b944a0bc","tid":1710981,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:35:46.000Z","msg":"香港人要靠自己，但係有外國幫手可以事半功倍<br />\n尤其是英國"},{"pid":"54bf5037b2673327041ffdb68bbe6515b031bc4c","tid":1710981,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:36:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a48f754e752691ec6b6cc08d4d66fe76add6bd1","tid":1710981,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:37:13.000Z","msg":"Agger<br />\n仲有加拿大"},{"pid":"064e8c096ad25048e8ccfee2c075e048e9d80197","tid":1710981,"uid":138382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:37:19.000Z","msg":"推 打左雖然未必有用 但係點都好過冇"},{"pid":"1208bd1905d1f1bda8ce308260500e7c709345b2","tid":1710981,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:38:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0d7da9cb189851f25fa79079dee4b4b0c46e519","tid":1710